title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 6 2022
description:
"Donald Trump is the ultimate target!" Former federal prosecutor Glenn Kirschner says Justice Department is "in a full sprint" to indict Trump for January 6th protest. Desperate Dems try to distract voters with Jan. 6 hearings. Biden is seething that he's polling lower than Trump. Frustrations and plummeting morale inside 1600 Pennsylvania Ave. amid growing fears that Biden administration parallels Jimmy Carter's malaise years. Naomi Wolf, bestselling author and columnist, joins Clay and Buck to weigh in on the transgender debate and covid. Buck reviews Top Gun: Maverick. Is Tom Cruise the greatest actor of all time?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
